ddle Ages, but was taken up in the 15th century and became common thereafter. It was borne by the American film star  Dorothy Lamour  (  1914–1996 , born  Dorothy Kaumeyer )."],"variants":[{"name":"Dorothee","meanings":["Usual English form of   Dorothea .  The name was not used in the Middle Ages, but was taken up in the 15th century and became common thereafter. It was borne by the American film star  Dorothy Lamour  (  1914–1996 , born  Dorothy Kaumeyer )."]},{"name":"Dorothie","meanings":["Usual English form of   Dorothea .  The name was not used in the Middle Ages, but was taken up in the 15th century and became common thereafter. It was borne by the American film star  Dorothy Lamour  (  1914–1996 , born  Dorothy Kaumeyer )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Dorothy Frye was born about 1288, in Hanslope, Buckinghamshire, England, United Kingdom as the daughter of Richard Frye. She had at least 4 sons with Phillip De Maunsell."},"et":{"Abt 1288–":"umbes 1288–Surnud","1288–Female":"1288–Surnud","1285–Male":"1285–Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1295–1361":"1295–1361","1312–Male":"1312–Surnud","1314–Male":"1314–Surnud","1318–Male":"1318–Surnud","1270–Male":"1270–Surnud","1285":"1285","1361":"1361","1295":"1295","1270":"1270","abt 1312":"umbes 1312","Abt 1295":"umbes 1295","about 1318":"umbes 1318","1314":"1314","1312":"1312","Abt 1288":"umbes 1288","about 1314":"umbes 1314","1288":"1288","1318":"1318","Northfield, Worcester, England":"Northfield, Worcestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Little Missenden, Buckinghamshire, England":"Little Missenden, Buckinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Of Missenden, Buckinghamshire, England":"Buckinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Hanslope, Buckinghamshire, England":"Hanslope, Buckinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","of Missenden, Bucks, Eng.":"Missenden, Hertfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1288–":"noin 1288–Kuollut","1288–Female":"1288–Kuollut","1285–Male":"1285–Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1295–1361":"1295–1361"